OL,3,CGlasgow fire: How dangerous are
OL,4,Clithium batteries in vapes?
OL,6,FWords by Producer Lois Smith
OL,8,FEmergency services were called to
OL,9,FGlasgow city centre on Sunday to
OL,10,Fattend a huge fire at a vape shop.
OL,12,FMore than 200 firefighters were at the
OL,13,Fscene as the blaze tore through Union
OL,14,FStreet, destroying a B-listed
OL,15,FVictorian building, closing
OL,16,Fbusinesses, and causing irreparable
OL,17,Fdamage.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
