OL,3,CGlasgow fire: How dangerous are
OL,4,Clithium batteries in vapes?
OL,6,FGlasgow Central Station, which was
OL,7,Fclose by, remains shut on Tuesday as
OL,8,Fsafety inspections are being carried
OL,9,Fout.
OL,11,FWhile the Scottish Fire and Rescue
OL,12,FService (SFRS) has said it cannot
OL,13,F"speculate on what happened" yet and
OL,14,Fhas confirmed that a full
OL,15,Finvestigation is underway, the fire is
OL,16,Fbelieved to have initially started in
OL,17,Fa vape shop on the ground floor of the
OL,18,Fbuilding.
OL,26,@uD@AOUuD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/17
