OL,3,CGlasgow fire: How dangerous are
OL,4,Clithium batteries in vapes?
OL,6,FA passer-by, Lamin Kongira, tried to
OL,7,Fextinguish the blaze in the vape shop,
OL,8,Fbut described being forced back by an
OL,9,F"explosion" from within the premises.
OL,10,FHe said he heard a more powerful blast
OL,11,Fshortly afterwards.
OL,13,FMost vapes use rechargeable lithium
OL,14,Fbatteries, which are high-energy, fast-
OL,15,Fto-charge, and last a long time.
OL,16,FHowever, they are also flammable and
OL,17,Fextremely sensitive to high
OL,18,Ftemperatures.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
