OL,3,CGlasgow fire: How dangerous are
OL,4,Clithium batteries in vapes?
OL,6,FSo what are Lithium-Ion batteries and
OL,7,Fhow dangerous are they? ITV News
OL,8,Fexplains.
OL,10,FWhat are Lithium-Ion batteries?
OL,12,FThere are three very common types of
OL,13,Fbattery: Alkaline, Nickel-Metal
OL,14,FHydride (NiMH), and Lithium-Ion (Li-
OL,15,Fion).
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
