PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1773180727
OL,3,CGlasgow fire: How dangerous are
OL,4,Clithium batteries in vapes?
OL,6,FAlkaline batteries are often the
OL,7,Fcheapest and the most common kind of
OL,8,Fbattery. You might find this type of
OL,9,Fnon-rechargeable battery in household
OL,10,Fitems such as your TV remote or smoke
OL,11,Fdetector.
OL,13,FNickel-Metal Hydride (NiMH) batteries
OL,14,Fare a common rechargeable alternative
OL,15,Fto alkaline batteries, whilst
OL,16,Fmaintaining low production and
OL,17,Fdevelopment costs.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
