OL,3,CGlasgow fire: How dangerous are
OL,4,Clithium batteries in vapes?
OL,6,FLithium-Ion (Li-ion), however, is the
OL,7,Fmost frequently used type of
OL,8,Frechargeable battery globally, with
OL,9,Fthe highest energy densities of any
OL,10,Fmodern battery type.
OL,12,FLi-ion batteries are lightweight,
OL,13,Fpowerful, and rechargeable, making
OL,14,Fthem well-suited for smartphones,
OL,15,Flaptops, and tablets. Vapes and e-
OL,16,Fbikes also use this type of battery.
OL,18,FAre these types of batteries dangerous?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
