OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1773180727
OL,3,CGlasgow fire: How dangerous are
OL,4,Clithium batteries in vapes?
OL,6,FLi-ion batteries are found in all
OL,7,Fkinds of household devices and are
OL,8,Fused safely by billions of people each
OL,9,Fday all over the world.
OL,11,FHowever, they are very high-energy,
OL,12,Fwhich means if they are not treated
OL,13,Fwith care, they can become damaged or
OL,14,Fhave a manufacturing fault - and catch
OL,15,Ffire.
OL,17,FAccording to the British Safety
OL,18,FCouncil, Li-ion battery fires "burn
OL,19,Fhotter and faster than conventional
OL,20,Ffires," which can cause serious damage
OL,21,Fto property and people.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
