OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1773180727
OL,3,CGlasgow fire: How dangerous are
OL,4,Clithium batteries in vapes?
OL,6,FFigures released by the London Fire
OL,7,FBrigade (LFB) indicate that last year
OL,8,Fthere were 206 ebike and escooter
OL,9,Ffires in London, with firefighters
OL,10,Fcalled to an average of 17 incidents
OL,11,Feach month.
OL,13,FMeanwhile, waste management company
OL,14,FBiffa reports that, between June and
OL,15,FOctober 2025, 180 fires across the
OL,16,Fcompany's UK estate were linked to
OL,17,Flithium-ion batteries ` many believed
OL,18,Fto originate from vapes.
OL,20,FGrowing concerns around vape shops
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
