OL,3,CGlasgow fire: How dangerous are
OL,4,Clithium batteries in vapes?
OL,6,FGlasgow Labour MSP Paul Sweeney said
OL,7,Fthat while it is "too early to
OL,8,Fapportion blame" for the Glasgow fire,
OL,9,F"this scandal makes it clear that a
OL,10,Fline must immediately be drawn in the
OL,11,Fsand for building controls".
OL,13,FHe continued: "It is as plain as day
OL,14,Fthat any business that uses lithium
OL,15,Fbatteries should be held to extremely
OL,16,Fhigh safety standards and inspected
OL,17,Fregularly.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
