PN,31510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1773180727
OL,3,CGlasgow fire: How dangerous are
OL,4,Clithium batteries in vapes?
OL,6,F"A vape shop is potentially a place
OL,7,Fthat is full of potential incendiary
OL,8,Fdevices, a powder keg if it is not
OL,9,Fmanaged properly."
OL,11,FWhat precautions should be taken when
OL,12,Fbuying and using vapes?
OL,14,FVapes and other lithium battery
OL,15,Fproducts should be purchased from
OL,16,Freputable sellers.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
