OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1773180727
OL,3,CGlasgow fire: How dangerous are
OL,4,Clithium batteries in vapes?
OL,6,FGreater Manchester Fire and Rescue
OL,7,FService (GMFRS) advises that vapes
OL,8,Fshould "meet UK product safety
OL,9,Fstandards and display the UKCA or
OL,10,FEuropean CE safety mark".
OL,12,F"Sub-standard or fake products can be
OL,13,Fa fire risk," it says.
OL,15,FManufacturers' instructions for use
OL,16,Fshould always be followed, it adds,
OL,17,Fand vapes should not be modified or
OL,18,Ftampered with.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
