PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1773180727
OL,3,CGlasgow fire: How dangerous are
OL,4,Clithium batteries in vapes?
OL,6,FDamaged vapes can be a fire risk, so
OL,7,Favoid dropping, puncturing, or
OL,8,Fexposing vapes and e-cigarettes into
OL,9,Fwater.
OL,11,FVapes should also be checked for signs
OL,12,Fof damage.
OL,14,F"If it feels hot, smells unusual or
OL,15,Fappears damaged, stop using it
OL,16,Fimmediately," say GMFRS.
OL,18,FCharging and storing vapes
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31513
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1773180727
OL,3,CGlasgow fire: How dangerous are
OL,4,Clithium batteries in vapes?
OL,6,FStoring and charging vapes correctly
OL,7,Fcan also help reduce the risk of fire.
OL,8,FVapes should be kept in a cool, dry
OL,9,Fplace - away from hot environments
OL,10,Fsuch as near vehicles or radiators.
OL,12,FGMFRS advises the public to "keep
OL,13,Fvapes and e-cigarettes away from metal
OL,14,Fobjects like coins or keys in pockets
OL,15,For bags. Contact with metal can cause
OL,16,Foverheating and a fire to start."
OL,18,F"Never use or charge vapes or e-
OL,19,Fcigarettes near medical oxygen,
OL,20,Femollient creams, or airflow
OL,21,Fmattresses", GMFRS adds.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31514
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1773180727
OL,3,CGlasgow fire: How dangerous are
OL,4,Clithium batteries in vapes?
OL,6,FVapes should, of course, also be kept
OL,7,Faway from children and pets.
OL,9,FThe LFB reminds consumers to only use
OL,10,Fthe charger that comes with the
OL,11,Fdevice, never leave a vape to charge
OL,12,Funattended or overnight, and to be
OL,13,Fcareful not to cover batteries that
OL,14,Fare on charge to reduce the risk of
OL,15,Foverheating.
OL,17,FSafely disposing of vapes
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
