PN,31515
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1773180727
OL,3,CGlasgow fire: How dangerous are
OL,4,Clithium batteries in vapes?
OL,6,FEarlier this month, Devon and Somerset
OL,7,FFire and Rescue Service issued a
OL,8,Fwarning that items containing Li-ion
OL,9,Fbatteries should never be disposed of
OL,10,Fin general waste, following "a rise in
OL,11,Ffires at waste depots and waste
OL,12,Fcollection vehicles linked to damaged
OL,13,Fbatteries".
OL,15,F"When thrown away in general waste,
OL,16,Fthey can be crushed or punctured
OL,17,Fduring collection", The Fire and
OL,18,FRescue Service say.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
