CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1773180727
OL,3,CGlasgow fire: How dangerous are
OL,4,Clithium batteries in vapes?
OL,6,F"This damage can cause short-
OL,7,Fcircuiting and overheating, triggering
OL,8,Fthermal runaway - a chain reaction
OL,9,Fthat releases energy uncontrollably
OL,10,Fand can result in intense, fast-
OL,11,Fspreading fires."
OL,13,FVapes should not be put in general
OL,14,Fwaste or recycling bins, but rather
OL,15,Freturned to the retailer or taken to
OL,16,Fyour local household waste recycling
OL,17,Fcentre.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
